        CH2["org:{id}:workflows"]
        CH3["org:{id}:dept:{id}"]
    end

    CH1 -->|subscribe| SSE_Handler
    CH2 -->|subscribe| WS_Handler
    CH3 -->|subscribe| WS_Handler
    SSE_Handler -->|event stream| SSE
    WS_Handler -->|JSON messages| WS
